.HP \w'void\ glFogCoordfv('u
.BI "void glFogCoordfv(GLfloat\ *\ " "coord" ");"
.SH "PARAMETERS"
.PP
\fIcoord\fR
.RS 4
Specifies a pointa ta a array containin a single value representin tha fog distance\&.
.RE
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
\fBglFogCoord\fR
specifies tha fog coordinizzle dat be associated wit each vertex n' tha current rasta position\&. Da value specified is interpolated n' used up in computin tha fog color (see
\fBglFog\fR())\&.
.SH "NOTES"
.PP
\fBglFogCoord\fR
is available only if tha GL version is 1\&.4 or pimped outer\&.
.PP
Da current fog coordinizzle can be updated at any time\&. In particular,
\fBglFogCoord\fR
can be called between a cold-ass lil call to
\fBglBegin\fR()
and tha correspondin call to
\fBglEnd\fR()\&.
